@throws AppException {@link INFRASTRUCTURE#ID_MODIFYCODETABLEDATA_TABLE_NAME_EMPTY ID_MODIFYCODETABLEDATA_TABLE_NAME_EMPTY} - if a code table name is empty. @throws AppException {@link INFRASTRUCTURE#ID_MODIFYCODETABLEDATA_LOCALE_EMPTY ID_MODIFYCODETABLEDATA_LOCALE_EMPTY} - if the localeIdentifier is empty. @throws AppException {@link INFRASTRUCTURE#ID_MODIFYCODETABLEDATA_DUPREC ID_MODIFYCODETABLEDATA_DUPREC} - if a code table header data is not unique. @throws AppException {@link INFRASTRUCTURE#ID_CHANGETABLEDATA_RECNOTFOUND ID_CHANGETABLEDATA_RECNOTFOUND} - if the record to changed cannot be found. @throws AppException {@link INFRASTRUCTURE#ID_RECORD_CHANGED ID_RECORD_CHANGED} - if the record has been changed by another user.
