linked in a hierarchy, its children codes will be updated as well. This
method does not allow you to change the parent code. To change the parent
code, you must call the modifyParentCode() method.

@param itemKey The name of the code table item and the table on which it
resides.
@param dtls The new code,description and annotation.

@throws AppException {@link INFRASTRUCTURE#ID_CHANGEITEM_RECNOTFOUND
ID_CHANGEITEM_RECNOTFOUND} - if the item to change cannot be found.
