{@link INFRASTRUCTURE#ID_CODETABLEADMIN_CHANGE_ITEM_DESCRIPTION_EMPTY
ID_CODETABLEADMIN_CHANGE_ITEM_DESCRIPTION_EMPTY} - if the new item does not
have a description.
@throws AppException {@link INFRASTRUCTURE#ID_CHANGEITEM_DUPREC
ID_CHANGEITEM_DUPREC} - if the item could not be changed because an item
with this name already exists on the table.
