     Returns all the version numbers of a specified template as a list.
The list contains versions for a given 'XSLTemplateID.templateID' and
'XSLTemplateID.locale' with country code and without country code.
i.e. If the XSLTemplateID provided includes the country part as locale
(i.e. 'en_US') the method returns the template versions with this locale
and also appends the versions without the country part (e.g. 'en') by
truncating the country part from the locale.
And If the XSLTemplateID provided does not contain the
country part (e.g. 'en'), the items in the template version list returned
by the method are repeated twice for a given locale.

@param key The ID for the specified template.

@return The version numbers of a specified template.

