     Returns all template versions for a specified XSLTemplateID.
If provided XSLTemplateID.locale contains country part
(i.e. 'en_US') and if at least one record is found with this locale
then the method returns only the template versions with this locale.
If no records found for specified locale containing country part
(i.e. 'en_US') the method returns the template versions without country
part (e.g. 'en'). Otherwise if provided XSLTemplateID.locale
does not contain country part (i.e. 'en') the method returns only the
template versions  without the country part (e.g. 'en').

