class.doc:
   Utility class that can be used to provide execution statistics for
application extension points. Statistics are made available via the
CuramExtensionPointsStats MBean.
<p>
Usage example:

<pre>
ExtensionPointMonitoring.executeExtensionPoint(&quot;myExtPoint&quot;, new Runnable() {
	public void run() {
		try {
			extensionPointMethod();
		} catch (RuntimeException e) {
			throw e;
		} catch (Exception e) {
			throw new RuntimeException(e);
		}
	}
});
</pre>

@author DMoraru

