     Set the flag indicating whether short name substitution should be performed
on object names.

@param shortNames A boolean which indicates if short names should be used.

Perform "short name substitution" on one word to bring its length down to no more than 18 characters. If the word consists of several words delimited by dot characters then each component word is shortened independently.
@param name Name to be processed. This must not be null.
@return Short name result in uppercase. If short names are switched off or if the word is no longer than 18 characters then the original word is returned in uppercase.
