     Gets the named resource applicable for the given locale. If no resource
is defined for that locale, a fall-back mechanism will be used to locate
an appropriate resource. For example, if the locale is "en_US", but there
is no matching resource for that locale, "en" will be checked next; if no
matching resource is found, a resource assigned to no locale will be used;
if no matching resource is found, an exception will be thrown.

