interface.doc:
   Implementors of this interface provide a unique signature for a particular
invocation. The example below shows a possible implementation.

<pre>
{@code
public class MyInvocationDifferentiator implements InvocationDifferentiator {
 public String createDifferentiator(String invocationTarget,
				Object... parameters) {
   if(invocationTarget.charAt(0) == 'i') {
    return String.valueOf(parameters[0]);
   }
   return null;
  }
 }
}
</pre>

